OL,3,CCycling athlete and grandad says heart
OL,4,Cstudy 'saved my life'
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent
OL,7,FVictoria Grimes has been speaking to
OL,8,FBrian Cookson OBE, a former athlete
OL,9,Fwho says his life was saved after
OL,10,Ftaking part in a British Heart
OL,11,FFoundation study.
OL,13,FA former athlete and grandad who
OL,14,Fsuffered a major health scare after
OL,15,Fhis heart rate soared above 200 beats
OL,16,Fper minute while cycling says being
OL,17,Fpart of a heart study at the time "has
OL,18,Fsaved my life."
