OL,3,CCycling athlete and grandad says heart
OL,4,Cstudy 'saved my life'
OL,6,FBrian Cookson OBE, from Whalley,
OL,7,FLancashire has dedicated his life to
OL,8,Fcycling, both as a competitor and as
OL,9,FPresident of British Cycling and Union
OL,10,FCycliste Internationale ` cycling's
OL,11,Fworld governing body.
OL,13,FThe 74-year-old never thought that the
OL,14,Fexercise he had been doing for the
OL,15,Flast six decades could be harming his
OL,16,Fheart. But while he was training at
OL,17,FManchester Velodrome in May 2024,
OL,18,FBrian started to "feel unwell."
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G2/8
OL,2,W,.!/  +.!/*%*%R,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
