OL,3,CCycling athlete and grandad says heart
OL,4,Cstudy 'saved my life'
OL,6,FBrian said: "My consultant rang me and
OL,7,Fsaid it was serious and to not do
OL,8,Fanything but walking for the next few
OL,9,Fweeks because I needed a device
OL,10,Ffitted."
OL,12,FHe had had an episode of ventricular
OL,13,Ftachycardia ` an abnormally fast
OL,14,Fheartbeat where the heart's main
OL,15,Fpumping chambers, are not able to pump
OL,16,Fblood around the body effectively. It
OL,17,Fcan led to cardiac arrest.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G4/8
