OL,3,CCycling athlete and grandad says heart
OL,4,Cstudy 'saved my life'
OL,6,F"I feel like being part of this
OL,7,FBritish Heart Foundation study has
OL,8,Fsaved my life", Brian said. "Without
OL,9,Fit, I might have carried on pushing
OL,10,Fmyself until something more serious
OL,11,Fhappened."
OL,13,FThe study has found athletes are more
OL,14,Flikely to have scaring on their hearts
OL,15,F- that means they are more likely to
OL,16,Fexperience abnormal rhythms which can
OL,17,Fbe dangerous.
