OL,3,CCycling athlete and grandad says heart
OL,4,Cstudy 'saved my life'
OL,6,FDr Peter Swoboda, Associate Professor
OL,7,Fin Cardiology and Consultant
OL,8,FCardiologist at the University of
OL,9,FLeeds: "If you have scaring, you're
OL,10,Ffour-and-a-half times more at risk of
OL,11,Fhaving one of these dangerous heart
OL,12,Frhythms.
OL,14,F"Cardiac arrest during sport is rare.
OL,15,FThe main message is to keep doing
OL,16,Fsport, but if you're having pain or
OL,17,Fparticularly breathless during
OL,18,Fexercise - get it checked out by a
OL,19,Fdoctor."
