OL,4,Cstudy 'saved my life'
OL,6,FBrian has since returned to cycling
OL,7,Fafter being fitted with the
OL,8,Fimplantable defibrillator, which will
OL,9,Fshock his heart if an abnormal rhythm
OL,10,Freoccurs.
OL,12,F"Nothing is going to stop me cycling.
OL,13,FI'm very happy to I can carry in doing
OL,14,Fit", David said. " But don't assume
OL,15,Fthat just because you're a regular
OL,16,Fsports person or athlete that you're
OL,17,Fimmune to problems."
